## 7. Exceptions
Deviations from defined role assignments (e.g., temporary combination of segregated duties) require documented risk acceptance with compensating controls per `exceptions-and-waivers.md.template`, approved by the [Security Officer] and [CEO].

## 8. Compliance, Monitoring & Enforcement
Role assignments are reviewed at management review and verified during internal audit and access recertification. Failure to perform assigned responsibilities is addressed per `../people/hr-security-policy.md.template`, including the HIPAA sanctions process.

